                          pyTray 
  
  Version 0.1

  What is it?
  -----------

  pyTray is a software for tracking crystallization experiments.

  The Latest Version
  ------------------

  Details of the latest version can be found on
  https://github.com/tschalch/pyTray. 

  Installation
  ------------

  For windows installation, copy the directory called "dist" into your location
  of choice. Use pyTray.exe to start the program.

